caspaxos/
├── CMakeLists.txt
├── cmake/
│   └── p2p_mesh_network-config.cmake.in
├── include/
│   └── p2p_mesh_network.hpp
├── lib/
│   └── libcaspaxos.a
│   └── libcaspaxos.so
├── src/
│   └── p2p_mesh_network.cpp
└── tests/
    └── p2p_mesh_network_tests.cpp

This CMake configuration provides:

Library Configuration:

 - Creates a shared/static library target
 - Sets up include directories
 - Configures installation rules

Test Configuration:

 - Automatically downloads and configures Google Test
 - Creates test executable
 - Provides verbose test target

Installation Support:

 - Generates and installs CMake config files
 - Creates proper installation rules
 - Supports CMake package finding

Build Features:

 - C++17 standard requirement
 - Compiler warnings enabled
 - Thread support included
 - Debug and Release configurations
